<section class="hero-landing" id="lowland-hero">
  <div class="page-description">
    <h1 class="pageTitle">Lowlands</h1>
    <p>People who have settled the coast, plains, and river banks. Lowlanders are more well-known and wide-spread than their highland counterparts. They armed themselves with iron weapons along with wooden side-arms such as throwing spears and
      shields and preferred wearing light to no armor. They were also known to use swivel-mounted and hand-held versions of cannons called <span class="italicized">lantaka</span>. They engaged in trade and waged war with each other and other surrounding thalassocracies. The
      majority of the lowlanders eventually either allied with the Spanish or were conquered. Descendants of lowland dwellers have, for the most part, adapted to the changes of time and, aside from the most destitute, can live relatively modern
      lives.</p>
  </div>
</section>


